{"tid":1732673,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"要救理大，一定要有一個國際背景嘅第三方組織出手救人，一定要令事件提升到國際層面","createTime":"2019-11-18T02:45:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T02:47:25.000Z","uid":103513,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"72d9e79f7d2133a39fe58dadca990296d07e0341","tid":1732673,"uid":103513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T02:45:01.000Z","msg":"唔係做失敗撚，大家認清楚形勢，內外環境<br />\n<br />\n內，單靠理大義士久守必失，物資會耗盡<br />\n外，尋晚到宜家咁多人圍魏都救唔到趙<br />\n<br />\n大家裝備差太太太遠，想強攻一點救人係不切實際，除非理大義士有本事造好多炸彈出嚟，否則我地攻幾多次都無用<br />\n<br />\n既然自己本土無辦法拆局，咁我地就只可以諗外援，所以我想大家一齊幫手諗諗計，點樣可以&amp;應該搵邊一個國際組織介入哩件事，例如令（我知好天馬行空）紅十字會入理大救人，令美軍入去救人（宣稱有美國公民被困？）<br />\n我好清楚明白上面嘅例子係好ff，所以先希望大家集思廣益，諗出更好嘅方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">重點係令理大事件擺上國際層面，令popo唔可以輕易出手</span></span>"},{"pid":"97ed60581fbbaacb91181630b4b7f1f12b220918","tid":1732673,"uid":207543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T02:47:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. 救人先 檢討後<br />\n2. 唔完美 理性講<br />\n3. 多體諒 少怪責<br />\n4. 遇分化 冷處理</span></span><br />\n辛苦曬po主同手足<br />\nbtw 幫推"},{"pid":"9088ada20e715f770756470d7187566f1be02f89","tid":1732673,"uid":125502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T02:47:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1NdgS8Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1NdgS8Y.jpg&h=fb14efa1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n老豆搵仔呼籲<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">你仲返工？去理大啦！</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不落單<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不譴責<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不退縮"}]}